---
title: Korean-inspired Irish Sirloin Steak with spicy mayo, sesame broccoli and roast potatoes
description: Aged Irish sirloin steak is coated in an Asian-inspired sticky and slightly sweet glaze in this fantastic fusion recipe. Paired with golden roasted potatoes and spicy sesame broccoli, the whole thing is tied together with a side of spicy mayo.
